  "texts": [
    "Unlike baseline methods, the distribution of TSGM-VP is almost identical to the original one.",
    "These figures provide an evidence of the excellent generation quality and diversity of our method.",
    "For TSGM-subVP, similar results are observed.",
    "Fig. 2:2Fig.2: The overall workflow of TSGM (see Section III-D).",
    "Our original learning objective is to approximate ∇ log p(x s 1:n |x 0 1:n-1), which is computationally prohibitive, with the conditional score network M θ (s, x s 1:n, x 0 1:n-1) using an MSE loss."
